Aap apne baare mein batain! Aap free time mein kya karte hain?
Kya aapne kuch dilchasp safar kiye hain ya koi aane waale safar ki planning ki hai?
Woh kya cheez hai jo hamesha aapko muskurahat de deti hai, chahe kuch bhi ho?
Kya aapko koi pasandida shauq ya aapko kuch pasandeeda activities hain jin par aapka dil lage?
Kya aapko khana pasand hai? Kya aapke pas koi pasandida restaurants hain ya koi khaas cuisine hai jo aap prefer karte hain?
Aakhri samay mein aapne koi behtareen kitaab ya film dekhi hai? Main hamesha naye recommendations ke liye tayyar hoon!
Agar aapko koi superpower chunni ho, to woh kya hogi aur kyun?
Apna dream job ya career kya hai ya aapki career ki kya ashaayen hain?
Kya aapne kabhi kuch seekhna ya koshish karna chaha hai lekin mauka nahi mila?
